surf_rez2
Made by Xbmann
Bonus 4: Spy Complex
Bonus 2: Muta


(T4, 5 stages, 4 bonuses)

Here it is, the long awaited sequel to the map I regretted uploading the most.
I tried to stay true to the original style of surf_rez while also applying
techniques and skills I've learned since them to branch off into something new.
Hopefully the map is as fun to surf as it was to make!
